# Electricity experiment automation
Automates upgrading of the Electricity experiment. DOES NOT PRESTIGE. Will purchase new wires and coils, and upgrade each wire of each coil until all are fully upgraded - assuming you have enough resources to do so

# Use
Requires the "Laboratory" to be open.
The "e" key will activate the main script. It will automatically activate other scripts as necessary and run through to upgrade all coils and wires, if resources run out the scripts will not stop.

# Requirements
The code is 3 scripts with a maximum 19 lines. The scripts can be viewed in the individual files as code with comments.
